race.comment: EARTH'S ABUNDANCE (10) resumes. Two runs in her debut campaign were good in strong maidens, fourth to Signature Scent on debut before running second to the Group performed Teine Aulelei at Bendigo. That form jumps off the page here and she maps for every chance. SMART AND MIGHTY (2) was good first up despite going under as favourite, only beaten a nose over 900m at Albury. He should be fitter for that and take plenty of catching here. SWEET FARNAN (12) resumes. She mixed her form in her debut campaign but the run two back was good. Watch the betting for a lead. NIC THE CASH (1) was hard in the market fresh but struggled on the heavy going. Expect he improves off that for the top yard. BRILLIANT BEAGLE (7) is back in trip but going well and has claims.
